channel.title: Good gnome stonghold agility thingy
channel.description:
Good, fast, accurate, mistake-proof(misses part of course), also supports basic conversations: "agility lvl?", "ag lvl" type of thing, prints out current status every loop, manages running, Supports multiple colors(not the exact same one everytime(good way to get banned) ), and smooth mouse.
I looked on Scar-Scripts, tested, they don't support all of these(not accuracy, mistake-proof, or convosations, some are not even good.)
